## 代码入口

```python
from ai_workflow.auto_reviewer import auto_review
review_result = auto_review(
    test_cases,        # test_cases.json 内容
    test_points,       # test_points.json 内容（可选）
    s4_risks          # S4 business_flow.md 解析结果（可选）
)
# review result['reviewer_a'] → 脚本数字统计
# review result['reviewer_b'] → 脚本数字统计
# review result['llm_review_a_semantic'] → LLM 语义审查结论
# review result['llm_review_b_semantic'] → LLM 覆盖率评判结论
# review result['recommendations'] → 必修/应改/可改分类
```

